<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tʿạlwạ tʿạlwạ yạ tʿạby̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tʿạlwạ tʿạlwạ yạ tʿạby̱ .. mn ạlʿạlm ạlḥzyn
 tʿạlwạ kẖdwạ ạlsʿạdẗ .. mn fạdy ạlʿạlmyn
 (hạtnswạ hmwm ạlʿạlm .. fy lḥẓẗ fy ṭrfẗ ʿyn)2
 fy lḥẓẗ fy ṭrfẗ ʿyn
 ạlqrạr- (dh jmạlh bạrʿ bạrʿ .. ạ̉jml mn kl ạlnạs
 nwr wjhh sạṭʿ sạṭʿ .. klh mḥbẗ wạ̹kẖlạṣ
 (msẖ lạqy zy ḥbyby yswʿ .. dwrt fy kl mkạn)2
 dwrt fy kl mkạn
 2- myn ymsḥ dmʿ ʿywny .. ạ̹lạ yswʿ ạlḥbyb
 dạ mạt ʿlsẖạn yfdyny .. mṭʿwn ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 (wqlby fy ʿz jrạḥh .. ylạqyh hw ạlṭbyb)2
 ylạqyh hw ạlṭbyb
 3- ạlnạs ymkn ynswnạ .. lkn yswʿ ạ̉myn
 fy ạlḍyq bytrkwnạ .. lkn yswʿ mʿyn
 (hw ạlly bydh mạsknạ .. fy ạlḍyq wfy ạlạ̉nyn)2
 fy ạlḍyq wfy ạlạ̉nyn
 4- ḥbyby mạlk ḥyạty .. ạlly whbny ạlḥyạẗ
 mʿạh lqyt nṣyby .. rwḥy hymạnẗ wyạh
 (wạ̉nạ mhmạ nẓrt lgẖyrh .. tsẖtạq rwḥy lrw̉yạh)2
 tsẖtạq rwḥy lrw̉yạh</lyrics>
<author>whyb nyqwlạ</author>
